Interface IDevice

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Headphones, Keyboard, Printer, SmartPhone, TV
    public interface IDevice
    This interface represents a generic device. Implementing classes should provide methods to access and modify basic information about the device such as its name, category, price, and quantity.
